                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18120408-78-defend849 t18120408-78-punish424"></join>
               Fined 1 s.
            </rs> and discharged.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Common Serjeant.</p>
